text: Sepat may refer to: * the Ancient Egyptian name for the regional divisions of the country. The Greek term nomos has been used in its place since the Ptolemaic period * Typhoon Sepat (disambiguation), the name of various weather disturbances in the north Pacific Ocean * Tanjung Sepat, Pahang, a town in Pahang in Malaysia * Tanjung Sepat, Selangor, a town in Selangor, Malaysia
title: Sepat
